message.content:
1) Exercise regularly
2) Eat a healthy, balanced diet
3) Limit alcohol consumption
4) Don't smoke or use tobacco products
5) Maintain a healthy weight
6) Get plenty of sleep (7-9 hours for adults)
7) Find ways to manage and reduce stress levels (practice relaxation techniques like meditation, deep breathing exercises or yoga)
8) Maintain strong social connections with friends and family 
9-out-of-repository
